               "text": "### Introduction\n\nWhen consulting a dictionary for the definition of \"word,\" we find the following description",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 0,
                     "uuid": "b71639bc-a91b-44a7-8d12-4ce942cb280d",
                     "text": "Cambridge Dictionary"
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ":"
            },
            {
               "text": "<ul class=\"citation\"><li><i>\"a single unit of language that has meaning and can be spoken or written:...\"</i></li> </ul>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": " "
            },
            {
               "text": "While this definition is precise, there remains an aspect worthy of further examination - one that is directly connected to the summation rules discussed in another text",
